idpt:inps-to-agid-graph a dcterms:Standard ;
    dcterms:description "Riconciliazione fra nomi INPS (CSV vigenti residenza + regime sede + serie storica) e URI AGID delle province italiane. Contiene: (a) skos:altLabel @it-x-inps con le forme nominali del CSV INPS vigenti residenza, (b) 106 istanze idpt:SedeINPS con prefLabel + notation + correspondsTo o aggregatesProvince verso le province AGID."@it ;
    dcterms:license <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> ;
    dcterms:source <https://www.inps.it/osservatorio> ;
    dcterms:title "Sidecar linking INPS ↔ AGID province + sedi"@it .

